name: SignatureComparison
description: The UiPath signature comparison model is used to determine the similarity between a pair of signature and suggest if the signatures are from the same author.
inputDescription: A pair of signature images in a list. Files formats accepted are png, and jpeg.
outputDescription: Similarity score (between 0 and 1) and a preliminary determination if the signatures are from the same author or different authors based on a defined threshold in a Json format.
projectDescription: Curated Models from UiPath to analyze images
